{"type": "article", "id": 14412, "title": "“巴雷”单椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-04T07:39:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000858o4dwIONu2T93GrYf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这把“巴雷”单椅（Ballerina chair）来自一个年轻的跨国设计团队Stimlig，由台湾和法国的设计师共同完成。既有东方榫接工艺，没有使用一颗钉子，也有来自西方芭蕾舞的灵感，如将扶手向上 2 °倾斜并延长了腿部，模拟了舞蹈演员手部轻举、指尖无限延伸的姿态，充满了古典的优雅。制作上采用山毛榉和黑胡桃两种实木，搭配出了四种颜色分别来自三大芭蕾舞剧《天鹅湖》、《睡美人》和《胡桃夹子》。目前还在众筹中，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/stimlig-ballerina\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261419457aDUZ4F30iIQWlBO.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"525\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141945IyKd1PVYW4jivflF.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"263\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.25047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261419460Ia1eCsHGKN6WcTd.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141946mnOtr9l5fTqS4uFM.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141946MyPqrm26HvupxR0A.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141947e63PoHc0VXSU4Gtf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141947SKnQDXrPLjsyez71.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}